  "text": "We assessed goodness-of-fit of the selected model by comparing predicted values with observed values using the R 2 and root mean square error (RMSE) statistics. Plots of predicted versus observed values and the goodness-of-fit statistics for the main models are provided in the Supporting information, Figs S4.1-S4.4. The Bayes factor was calculated for the results of the main analysis [CITATION_1] .",
